Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是基於大量調查與驗證而製作的虛構作品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本動畫以發生了大地震的首都區為假想舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在動畫中 會有部分與實際相出入的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原作為追求逼真效果 經過了充分的模擬測試
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:01:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的煙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切 都不是在做夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:12.11,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,660)\fad(300,0)}「燃燒、橋」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那個大姐姐去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道 別樣樣都來問我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 大不了我們兩個自己回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 不知道電話能打了不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}無法接收到信號
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徹底不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望爸爸媽媽都沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對嗎姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道 電話打不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你別樣樣都問我沒聽懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 兩位小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子一餓就會容易心浮氣躁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 早餐駕到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫真理就行了 悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是飯團
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來你也吃點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有飲料哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些是哪兒來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得以前聽說非常時期便利店會派發食品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以去看了下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來沒見你 還以為你先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見我不在 未來覺得寂寞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我做個保證吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後我再也不擅自離開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.84,0:04:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪兒的時候一定先告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做到這份上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡不是還有孩子在等你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.55,0:04:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有我們的話你不是能早點回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.31,0:04:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 也許你說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們家的方向不是一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也算是某種緣分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能照顧你們多久就多久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會拖累你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.45,0:04:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把這個吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:05:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子一餓連人都變得疑神疑鬼了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.77,0:05:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補充能量 才能奮鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 開動開動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梅子味的 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的是鮭魚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這天熱的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.13,0:05:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也要酷暑難耐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看快四十了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理姐有點男人婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人也老這麼說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過未來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話太直
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:05:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.35,0:06:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸虧你昨天買了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 讓我們來瞧瞧新聞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看久了電池撐不住 快看快關哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面繼續報道由地震造成的都內災情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有交通設施均處癱瘓 尚無恢復的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一級交通管制啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄰接多摩川 246國道及7號環線的內部地區
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有機動車輛禁止通行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止 已確認遇難者人數為843名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另有大量失蹤 重輕傷人員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計死亡人數將繼續增加
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了這麼多人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}目前有部分地區火災尚未停止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在場及附近的群眾盡快向避難所轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外目前有大量受災群眾正在步行回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來聽一下京阪大學災害研究所的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村田憲明教授對今後事態的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據預測本次首都直下型地震已造成了多達650萬的群眾無法回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今後餘震的變化將如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預計今後三天內將間歇地發生5級以上的餘震
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.85,0:07:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然大家都在走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前這狀況 根本不知道電車要到什麼時候才能動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.35,0:07:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大姐姐 我們也走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃過飯團我有力氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.69,0:08:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這兒離世田谷太遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實不是幾步就能回得去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台場成了死島?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋燒了 其他地方又走不通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們不是完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.17,0:08:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兒說不定要沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 再怎麼樣這麼大的地方是不可能沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 台場是人造地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 這兒有陰涼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩了 水和吃的都沒帶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 這裡也有居民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援馬上就會到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對 能一家人在一起就很幸運了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見爸爸媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走走看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想盡快回爸爸媽媽那兒去對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是海上保安廳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在將用水上巴士進行受災人員轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去日出碼頭方向的人請在前方公園旁邊的碼頭等待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}太好了 看來能坐船去日出碼頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去千葉方向的人請在…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.30,0:09:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道不穿什麼涼鞋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是跟腳打滑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊看上去很疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.77,0:09:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡有孩子這個就成了必備啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創可貼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是青蛙哦 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姐是青蛙大聖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙大聖?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.45,0:10:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了你別多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我借用下創口貼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣 不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還走得動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.78,0:10:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 實在不行了我背你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人會背你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過要是受不了就說哦 我會背你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體力方面我有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人能走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是這種精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別硬撐 慢慢走就行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  我們真的能坐上船嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.34,0:11:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多人都想坐船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.44,0:11:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐不上嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先去了再說啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒問題啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理姐好樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  這叫積極向上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 3 2 起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了 幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以離開媽媽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.60,0:12:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.32,0:12:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停船的地方就在前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好善良啊 真理姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也叫愛管閒事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是剛剛約好離開團體時要好好關照一聲的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:13:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦 真理姐姐做了件好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去東京國際會展中心（Big Sight）的請直走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.05,0:13:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘船去濱松方向的請在前面的十字口左轉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.08,0:13:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為想回家的人都只能往這邊走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意不要走散了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來也牽手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事啦 又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟緊了哦 別走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.46,0:14:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.12,0:14:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擋路了啊 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴 真理姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 別傻站在那
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.27,0:14:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是牽著手走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.27,0:15:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.75,0:15:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像爆炸似的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高架居然塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊 橋不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能坐船了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.21,0:16:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本船即將進行落水者的救援工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.72,0:16:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家去乘水上巴士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.65,0:16:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別乘這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不要放手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真理姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:16:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.23,0:17:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.37,0:17:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船馬上要出航了 請讓體力不支者優先上船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能等下班船了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之過去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.66,0:18:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想乘船的請等下一班
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一班看來不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的小孩 快上船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 媽媽也請快一些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家等待下一班船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家冷靜些 這樣太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然情況不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們乘到船了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你反應真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人一說「媽媽」你馬上「是」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 在我老公死了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.78,0:19:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越來越堅強了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我一個人 也要好好撫養小雛長大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看 大橋一直在燒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是油罐車著火了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 有人落水了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是晚一步上了那條船…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 這邊也起浪了
